{"tid":2050088,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"信報：17區搞聯合大會講國安法 民政署唔派秘書難站得住腳 2002年討論23條時照樣提供支援","createTime":"2020-06-04T01:52:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-04T02:21:08.000Z","uid":48083,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"d990eff430fbf956d40829da49ef648828810f2d","tid":2050088,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T01:52:26.000Z","msg":"儘管這次17區聯合會議討論的是與市民息息相關的「香港國安法」，政府亦無打算派DO參與。民政事務總署回覆查詢時解釋，《國家安全法》不屬地方行政範圍，議程不符合《區議會條例》訂明的區議會職能，故區議會秘書處不會提供支援⋯<br />\n<br />\n2002年建制討論支持23條<br />\n<br />\n翻查資料，特區政府以《國家安全法》不屬地方行政範圍為由，拒為聯合會議提供支援似難站得住腳，事關區議會過往曾研究非民生政治議題，官員均未有缺席。例如2002年多個由建制派主導的區議會就《基本法》23條立法進行討論，當時18區區議會主席更向政府提交聯署信表示支持立法。難道當年的23條立法屬地方行政，今天的「香港國安法」就不是？<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www2.hkej.com/landing/mobArticle2/id/2485312\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Flanding%2FmobArticle2%2Fid%2F2485312&d=Fi4Me5dMHeyo7M%2BwlVraY0Ka%2BtsrA1nil%2BMmquCK26s%3D&h=4a0a5985\" target=\"_blank\">http://www2.hkej.com/landing/mobArticle2/id/2485312</a>"},{"pid":"a80fcebf2f9a76cbfaa4fc7def53232fb370c03c","tid":2050088,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T01:57:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/UASSMEQ5NEQ62DSTACK7H73SDE.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FUASSMEQ5NEQ62DSTACK7H73SDE.gif&h=c118adaf&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4916aa1ae94ac3e8ebd9139dc4a8afe64e68424a","tid":2050088,"uid":97398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T02:08:56.000Z","msg":"02年個時仲未有戰狼concept"},{"pid":"5163dce84bbbf1ed7ad861d254d60ef3e5115562","tid":2050088,"uid":3149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T02:21:08.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/as